<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Scala on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/scala/</link><description>Recent content in Scala on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/scala/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>NullPointerException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/null-pointer6/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/null-pointer6/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you try to call a method or access a field on a null object reference. While Scala encourages using &lt;code&gt;Option&lt;/code&gt; instead of null, interoperating with Java libraries can still produce null references.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Java methods returning null&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uninitialized nullable variables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Not handling Option properly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forgetting that a method might return null&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Not handling null from Java
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; javaMethod&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// might be null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;toUpperCase&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use Option or null check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; javaMethod&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Some&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;n&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;n&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;toUpperCase&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;None&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;No name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Using get on None
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; opt&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; opt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;get &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NoSuchElementException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use getOrElse or pattern match
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; opt&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;None&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; opt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;getOrElse&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-scala" data-lang="scala"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Null from Java library
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; java.util._
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ArrayList&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ArrayList&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; item &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; list&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;get&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;item&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;length&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Uninitialized var
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;s&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;toUpperCase&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Option.get on None
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; map &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Map&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;map&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;get&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;).&lt;/span&gt;get &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NoSuchElementException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/class-cast"&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/scala/match-error4"&gt;MatchError&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>